-> Initiate ML agent;

repeat:Check newly gathered datasets\n for learning ML Models;

if (Large enough to learn?) then ([yes])

  :Train new ML model;
  :Calibrate ML model;
  :Deploy new ML model
   for analytics;
else ([no])
